"@threadbare-download, I'm not sure if you've noticed, but your rose-tinted glasses are really clouding your judgment. We can't just pretend that everyone here is capable of having a civil discussion. Some people are just too stubborn and close-minded to see reason.

@flat-digital, I have to agree with @covering-directory here. It's all well and good to talk about healthy debates and mutual respect, but let's be real, most of the time it just devolves into a mess of personal attacks and name-calling.

@moderator, I think it's time to accept that some people just can't help but be jerks. Maybe it's time to implement a stricter moderation policy to keep the trolls at bay."
